&reftitle.description;
public boolZipArchive::replaceFile stringfilepath intindex intstart0 intlengthZipArchive::LENGTH_TO_END intflags0
Replace file in ZIP archive with a given path.
&zip.filename.separator;

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     8.3.0, PECL zip 1.22.1

      ZipArchive::FL_OPEN_FILE_NOW was added.




     8.3.0, PECL zip 1.22.2

      ZipArchive::LENGTH_TO_END and ZipArchive::LENGTH_UNCHECKED were added.

  &reftitle.examples;


     This example opens a ZIP file archive
     test.zip and replaces index 1 entry
     with /path/to/index.txt.


     Open and replace


<?php
$zip = new ZipArchive;
if ($zip->open('test.zip') === TRUE) {
    $zip->replaceFile('/path/to/index.txt', 1);
    $zip->close();
    echo 'ok';
} else {
    echo 'failed';
}
?>
